org.openimaj.knn

Class CoordinateKDTree<T extends Coordinate>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.knn.CoordinateKDTree<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of Coordinate.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoordinateIndex<T>

    public class CoordinateKDTree<T extends Coordinate>
extends Object
implements CoordinateIndex<T>
    Implementation of a simple KDTree with range search. The KDTree allows fast search for points in relatively low-dimension spaces.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
